product.title: Blowout Brush, IG INGLAM 4 in 1 Hair Dryer Brush Set, Negative Ion Detachable Blow Dryer Brush Set & Styler Volumizer Hair Styling Tools, Gray
product.description:
IG INGLAM Hair Dryer Brush/Smoothing Brush/Hair Dryer/Volumizer Four in One, Blowout Brush Set Multi-Temperature Settings, Detachable Design suitable for families, business trips, weddings, and vacations, allowing you to design the hairstyle you want as you want! The exquisite packaging also allows you to use it as a gift for friends, family, or other loved ones.

About this item:

Product Name: IG INGLAM BLOW OUT BRUSH DRYER SET

Item Weight: 3.4 lb

Item Condition: New

Cord length: 6 FT

Rating Voltage: 125V~ 60Hz

Rating Power: 1100W

Key Features:

1. Negative ion care

2. Polyester bag for easy store

3. Three temperature settings- High/ Low/ Cool

4. Detachable design for travel

5. Multifunctional - Drying/Straightening/Volume/Curling

6. Nylon bristles and Nylon pins Design reduces static and leaves healthy and shiny hair.

Pre-Styling Dryer-

The hair dryer can speed up drying and has no extreme heat. It provides gentle airflow and releases negative ions to avoid damage to the hair. It is an essential tool for drying and styling hair efficiently.

3.5 Inch Oval Styling Brush-

This brush features a nylon tufted design that prevents tangles and helps straighten curls. It can also be used to create voluminous curls or waves.

Smoothing Brush-

Creates a smoother and straightener with less frizz and fewer flyaways.

Volumizer Diffuser-

This brush head helps create flowing curls and waves. Makes the hairstyle more fluffy and charming. Has a three-dimensional feel.

Has a three-dimensional feel. * Versatile Styling Accessories - The hair appliances includes multiple attachments: A smoothing brush, oval brush, blow dryer, and volumizer diffuser, allowing you to achieve diverse looks, from smooth and straight to bouncy curls, enhancing your styling options.
 * Easy Change Design for Effortless Styling - Just press the button to switch between brush heads, making it a breeze to create everyday sleek styles, romantic curls, or fluffy volume—because every woman deserves effortless beauty.
 * 3 Mode Heat Settings - Temperature control allows you to choose the optimum one to fit your hair type, with 3 adjustable heating levels to achieve endless looks and styles. Low temperature or low wind for thin and fine hair. The cool setting for locking in your hair styling. High temp or high wind for thick and coarse hair.
 * Negative Ions Technology - Featured by a built-in generator that releases negative ions, the hair dryer brush head made of nylon bristles and nylon pins helps to maintain the neutral electric charge on the hair surface, reducing static and leaving healthy and shiny hair.
 * Professional Grade Safety Assurance - Engineered for worry-free use, this styling tool is ETL Certified and complies with rigorous U.S. safety regulations, ensuring reliable performance without compromising on protection.
